<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="English_Language_Grammar_Books">English Language Grammar Books</span></h2>
<p>The following books are available in English, through Amazon:
</p>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0415472156/ref%3das_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=217145&amp;creative=399369&amp;creativeASIN=0415472156">Basic Chinese: A Grammar and Workbook</a></li></ul>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0415160391/ref%3das_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=217145&amp;creative=399373&amp;creativeASIN=0415160391">Intermediate Chinese: A Grammar and Workbook</a></li></ul>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1933330899/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=217145&amp;creative=399373&amp;creativeASIN=1933330899">Basic Patterns of Chinese Grammar</a></li></ul>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0415372615/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=217145&amp;creative=399369&amp;creativeASIN=0415372615">Chinese: An Essential Grammar, Second Edition</a></li></ul>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/7802006473/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=217145&amp;creative=399373&amp;creativeASIN=7802006473">Common Chinese Patterns 330</a></li></ul>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0520066103?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=0520066103">Mandarin Chinese: A Functional Reference Grammar</a></li></ul>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0415700108?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=0415700108">Modern Mandarin Chinese Grammar: A Practical Guide</a></li></ul>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0071635262/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=217145&amp;creative=399377&amp;creativeASIN=0071635262">Schaum's Outline of Chinese Grammar</a></li></ul>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1444109138/ref%3das_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=217145&amp;creative=399369&amp;creativeASIN=1444109138">Yufa!</a></li></ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Chinese_Language_Grammar_Books">Chinese Language Grammar Books</span></h2>
<p>The following books are available for order in China, through Amazon.cn and its Chinese partner, Joyo (卓越):
</p>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.cn/mn/detailApp/ref=as_li_ss_tl?_encoding=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-23&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;asin=B001N6R7DI&amp;camp=536&amp;creative=3132&amp;creativeASIN=B001N6R7DI">HSK语法精讲精练</a> (HSK Grammar)</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.cn/mn/detailApp/ref=as_li_ss_tl?_encoding=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-23&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;asin=B002ZNK7JE&amp;camp=536&amp;creative=3132&amp;creativeASIN=B002ZNK7JE">汉语常用格式330例</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.cn/gp/product/B004WA6JSQ/ref%3das_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-23&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=536&amp;creative=3132&amp;creativeASIN=B004WA6JSQ">汉语语法百项讲练</a></li></ul>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.cn/mn/detailApp/ref=as_li_ss_tl?_encoding=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-23&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;asin=B0041UGAJU&amp;camp=536&amp;creative=3132&amp;creativeASIN=B0041UGAJU">简明汉语语法学习手册</a> (Chinese Grammar Without Tears)</li></ul>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.cn/mn/detailApp?_encoding=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-23&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;asin=B001DUFS3A&amp;camp=536&amp;creative=3132&amp;creativeASIN=B001DUFS3A">实用汉语语法</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.cn/mn/detailApp?_encoding=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-23&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;asin=B003YJGCSS&amp;camp=536&amp;creative=3132&amp;creativeASIN=B003YJGCSS">实用现代汉语语法</a></li></ul>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.cn/mn/detailApp?_encoding=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-23&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;asin=B001J0ADWA&amp;camp=536&amp;creative=3132&amp;creativeASIN=B001J0ADWA">外国人实用汉语语法(中英文对照)</a> (A Practical Chinese Grammar for Foreigners)</li></ul>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.cn/mn/detailApp?_encoding=UTF8&amp;tag=allset-23&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;asin=B001198GSW&amp;camp=536&amp;creative=3132&amp;creativeASIN=B001198GSW">现代汉语八百词</a></li>
